== 员工 ==
毕马威美国分所被认为是对于母亲上班族最好的十家企业之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.workingmother.com/web?service=direct%2F1%2FViewArticlePage%2FdlinkFullFeaturedArticle&sp=601&sp=94 |title=Working Mother |accessdate=2020-09-12 |archive-date=2010-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100327174157/http://www.workingmother.com/web?service=direct%2F1%2FViewArticlePage%2FdlinkFullFeaturedArticle&sp=601&sp=94 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这里同时也是财富杂志百家雇主当中排名第71的企业<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/bestcompanies/2008/full_list/ |title=Fortune Magazine's 100 Best Companies to Work For |accessdate=2009-02-23 |archive-date=2009-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090218193919/http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/bestcompanies/2008/full_list/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同时，毕马威也是《Training》杂志在125家企业中评选出的五佳员工培训企业。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kpmgcareers.com/whoweare/training.pdf |title=Extract from Training Magazine |accessdate=2009-02-23 |archive-date=2009-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090320164904/http://www.kpmgcareers.com/whoweare/training.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根据College Grad.com的统计，毕马威是美国大学生心目当中“四大”里的最佳雇主<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.collegegrad.com/press/big-four.shtml |title=College Grad.com |accessdate=2009-02-23 |archive-date=2008-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205082505/http://www.collegegrad.com/press/big-four.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年，这家企业又被推选为“五十大职业生涯起步企业”之一<ref>[http://bwnt.businessweek.com/interactive_reports/career_launch_2008/index.asp Best Places to Launch a Career] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080907235329/http://bwnt.businessweek.com/interactive_reports/career_launch_2008/index.asp |date=2008-09-07 }}</ref>。

毕马威也荣获了《[[时代周刊|时代周刊]]》评选的2008年最佳雇主。这也是它连续第四年进入该评比的前三名。但是也有传言说，加入可以在评比中取得好的名次，参与调查的员工可以得到额外的两天假期。有人质疑，这种做法会影响评选的客观性。

在金融危机的影响下，毕马威于2009年开始试行4天工作制，这也是为了避免大规模的裁员。但即便如此，仍有超过100名员工被辞退。其中有一些员工指责公司并未能及时宣布裁员的信息。

2008年10月，毕马威被加拿大传媒集团授予“加拿大100大雇主头衔”。该月晚些时候，这家企业又被《多伦多星报》评为了“多伦多最佳雇主”之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eluta.ca/top-employer-kpmg|title=Reasons for Selection, 2009 Canada's Top 100 Employers Competition|accessdate=2009-02-23|archive-date=2009-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090301010254/http://www.eluta.ca/top-employer-kpmg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
